{"tid":2037603,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"3800億市值網易據報下周二招股","createTime":"2020-05-27T05:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T05:41:34.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"197c2d610d93d1eef9ca8a09cb727a0aee775180","tid":2037603,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2650000/2653848/20200527__v2_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2650000%2F2653848%2F20200527__v2_1024.png&h=48d27cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網易（美：NTES）據報搶閘下周公開招股，將快過京東（美：JD） 掛牌。消息指，網易的集資額較早前市傳的進一步增加，最新介乎20億至30億美元。<br />\n<br />\n本地傳媒引述消息人士報道， 網易將在下周二至周五（6月2日至5日）公開招股，集資額較早前市傳的10億至20億美元（約78億至156億港元）進一步增加，介乎20億至30億美元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，京東亦已初步敲定在6月8日至11日公開招股。若按照上述時間表，投資者認購網易的資金將可及時回籠，再認購京東。<br />\n<br />\n網易對消息不願置評。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網易暫時係中概股第五大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f54041f6a838ee62a98cfb7370db43e6a33978","tid":2037603,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"又有機會了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}